解釋<br />\n<br />\n中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"申請美國VISA就好似比人當審犯咁<br />\n堂堂高尚香港人要比千幾蚊同人排隊拎VISA<br />\n為左保住個拒簽率，你唔好彩又會比人拒簽<br />\n諗起都激鬼氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T05:53:20.000Z","msg":"但是<br />\n隔離鄰國中國大陸人排除申請小美國綠卡條隊一早都超過十年！大把人願意做美國人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb3e30a4c476d680036d3ccd24d59c4355b6fa9","tid":649584,"uid":130113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"免簽數多又唔代表好"},{"pid":"13fba04afe72bfe6e5706676ac749c8c630a8236","tid":649584,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bb3e30a4c476d680036d3ccd24d59c4355b6fa9","tid":649584,"uid":130113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"免簽數多又唔代表好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T13:28:32.000Z","msg":"點解呢？<br />\n入境署邊境控制差唔好賴大家要求鬆章"}]}